Félix Moati https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/F%C3%A9lix_Moati 0 Félix Moati (born 24 May 1990) is a French actor, film director and screenwriter. He is the son of the journalist and filmmaker Serge Moati. Félix_Moati ( born 24_May_1990 ) is a_French_actor , film_director_and_screenwriter .
